{"tid":2211052,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"初中歷史書　雅典民主硬插基本法　","createTime":"2020-09-21T01:22:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-21T12:44:30.000Z","uid":184679,"like":12,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"8ff0eada1d5d6042f30f8c268cefd64359b2d762","tid":2211052,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T01:22:13.000Z","msg":"《明報》&mdash; 初中歷史書 雅典民主扣基本法 連繫港人選舉權 教師質疑強加不符教學需要<br />\n<br />\n繼早前部分高中通識新書刪減三權分立、公民抗命等內容，本報發現有今年新版的初中歷史課書本，新增《基本法》內容，包括講解古代雅典民主政治制度時，插入基本法條文稱港人有選舉權和守法義務；講述公元7世紀伊斯蘭教起源歷史及教義時，就引述基本法稱本港有宗教信仰自由。有歷史科教師認為，古代尚未出現基本法，學習古代歷史強加現今事情，未必符合教學需要。教育局就稱，歷史科插入基本法內容合理。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=406277\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D406277&d=nIll2RoSQXmni3IMQi%2BZogEDdXZq%2B7ycbDpBQOFx8Mg%3D&h=01fb3073\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D406277&h=1caef549\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=406277</a>"},{"pid":"5abb20e85eb22e43961fd396ea1836300f05f108","tid":2211052,"uid":55493,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T01:25:57.000Z","msg":"噉仆街啦，噉城邦派呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雅典城邦喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/asset